  "description": "<p><strong>历经几番波折之后，中国移动2013年4G招标终于正式启动。</strong>日前，中国移动在其采购与招标网站上公布了本年度4G网络工程的主设备集中采购招标公告。公告称，中国移动此次集中采购涉及全国31个省市，采购规模约为20.7万个基站，共计55万载扇。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2dbc5a23/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242315.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A84G%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8+20%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%BA%E7%AB%99%E8%80%83%E9%AA%8C%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%95%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242315.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A84G%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8+20%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%BA%E7%AB%99%E8%80%83%E9%AA%8C%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%95%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242315.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A84G%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8+20%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%BA%E7%AB%99%E8%80%83%E9%AA%8C%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%95%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242315.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A84G%E6%8B%9B%E6%A0%87%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8+20%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%BA%E7%AB%99%E8%80%83%E9%AA%8C%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%95%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F2423