  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242314.htm", 
  "description": "<p> <strong>硬盘生产商西部数据公司周一称，该公司旗下全资子公司HGST将收购陷入困境的企业级固态硬盘生产商Stec，</strong>这项交易将使其成为迅速增长的固态硬盘行业 中的顶级从业公司之一。尽管固态硬盘这种存储设备的价格较高，但与传统硬盘相比，固态硬盘的速度要快得多。目前，这一行业目前正呈现出繁荣发展的景象。 </p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2dbc5a22/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242314.htm&amp;t=%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%A8%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE3.4%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%AD%E5%9B%BA%E6%80%81%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%95%86Stec\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242314.htm&amp;t=%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%A8%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE3.4%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%AD%E5%9B%BA%E6%80%81%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%95%86Stec\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242314.htm&amp;t=%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%A8%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE3.4%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%AD%E5%9B%BA%E6%80%81%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%95%86Stec\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242314.htm&amp;t=%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%A8%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE3.4%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%AD%E5%9B%BA%E6%80%81%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%95%86Stec\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242314.htm&amp;t=%E8%A5%BF%E9%83%A8%E6%9