  "description": "<p><strong>据国外媒体报道，受大市下跌、分析师下调iPhone销量预期目标和苹果目标价以及员工士气低落等因素影响，苹果在周一的股市交易中再度跌破400美元关口。</strong>截至美东时间周一下午1点09分，苹果股票跌至399.78美元，跌幅为3.3%。截至上周五收盘，苹果股票今年累计跌幅为22%；同期标准普尔500股指上涨12%。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2dbc5a21/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242313.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%B7%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B4400%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%EF%BC%9AiPhone%E8%AE%A2%E5%8D%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E6%B6%88%E5%87%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242313.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%B7%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B4400%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%EF%BC%9AiPhone%E8%AE%A2%E5%8D%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E6%B6%88%E5%87%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242313.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%B7%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B4400%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%EF%BC%9AiPhone%E8%AE%A2%E5%8D%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E6%B6%88%E5%87%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242313.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%B7%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B4400%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%EF%BC%9AiPhone%E8%AE%A2%E5%8D%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E6%B6%88%E5%87%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242313.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%B7%E8%B7%8